er retains more\ncustomers than a plain GSP mechanism and also yields better long-run utilities\nto the search engine and the advertisers.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 25 Jun 2009 18:25:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 30 Jun 2009 11:31:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-06-30"}
