sible peak between 10 and 100\nMyrs, and an average value of SFR ~ 0.6 or 0.7 M_{sun} yr^{-1} (for metallicity\nZ=0.02 or 0.05 respectively) over the last 400 Myrs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 26 Jun 2009 04:22:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 26 Aug 2009 21:15:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-10-02"}
