sity of states presents strong resonances at finite energies, which\nleads to steps in the scanning tunneling currents and to suppression of the\nFano factor.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 26 Jun 2009 08:19:52 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 6 Jul 2009 16:47:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-10-06"}
