nd the observed silicate\nfeature is found if all three phenomena occur in such an environment, existing\nas close as 10 pc from the central engine.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 26 Jun 2009 09:32:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 10 Jul 2009 16:23:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-02-11"}
